    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "After some careful debugging, the answer is yes, instantsearch and Firebase can coexist in the same app. `search.start()` was activated within `window.onload` which seemed to load after Firebase. When I instead put `search.start()` inside of `$(document).ready` then instantsearch works alongside Firebase.",
