    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The issue here was probably more to do with the fact of mixing document.ready and window.only since they'll be called at the same time almost, but not exactly, which might cause some undefined behaviour. If you have a project somewhere with this situation, it would be nice to see if we can work around the problem without changing your code",
